<h1 style="color: #2F5496; border-bottom: 2px solid #2F5496; padding-bottom: 5px; font-size: 24pt;">PorciTrack — Final Evaluation & Submission</h1>
<p style="font-size: 12pt;"><b>Group 7 | Systems Analysis & Design II</b><br>
<b>WEEK 15 — FINAL EVALUATION & SUBMISSION</b></p>
<p style="font-size: 11pt;">PorciTrack has successfully reached v1.0 Production Readiness. This document serves as the executive summary and architectural overview of the final system, finalizing all project deliverables for SADII.</p>

<br>
<h2 style="color: #2F5496; font-size: 16pt;">1. Final System Architecture</h2>
<p style="font-size: 11pt;">The system encapsulates a dual-portal farm management environment utilizing the Laravel framework, optimized for modern agricultural requirements.</p>

<table border="1" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; font-size: 11pt; border-color: #A6A6A6;">
    <tr bgcolor="#D9E1F2" style="font-weight: bold; color: #1F3864;">
        <th style="width: 25%;">Technology Category</th>
        <th style="width: 75%;">Stack & Implementation</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td><b>Backend Infrastructure</b></td>
        <td>Laravel 12 (PHP 8.4) with Object-Relational Mapping (Eloquent ORM) interfacing with a relational MySQL / MariaDB database.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td><b>Frontend UI/UX</b></td>
        <td>Blade Templating Engine combined with Tailwind CSS / Custom Glassmorphism styling. Logic is handled via Vanilla JS scoped into a global <code>PT_APP</code> object to prevent conflicts. Mobile interfaces utilize Progressive Web App (PWA) methodologies.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td><b>Third-Party Integrations</b></td>
        <td><b>Google Gemini AI:</b> Synchronizes regional biosecurity threats.<br><b>DOMPDF:</b> Generates and exports enterprise financial and health reports.<br><b>SweetAlert2 & Boxicons:</b> Enhances UI interactivity.</td>
    </tr>
</table>

<br>
