<h2 style="color: #2F5496; font-size: 14pt;">3. Rubric Evaluation</h2>
<ul style="font-size: 11pt;">
    <li><b>Overall System Quality (50%):</b> The application demonstrates high stability, responsive UI design (dark/light mode glassmorphism), and robust error handling. Complex features like AI integrations and real-time notifications operate smoothly.</li>
    <li><b>Completeness of Outputs (30%):</b> All required modules (Backend, Auth, Reporting, Alerts, Inventory, Task Management) are fully functional and properly seeded.</li>
    <li><b>Professionalism (20%):</b> The codebase is cleanly organized, GitHub commits are properly attributed to team members, and the documentation adheres strictly to professional, enterprise-grade formatting standards.</li>
</ul>

